Name: hyde-slimmer
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Html compression as post processor
Home-page: http://github.com/dstufft/hyde-slimmer
Author: Donald von Stufft
Author-email: donald.stufft@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: Hyde Slimmer
        ------------
        
        This module is a wrapper around Peter Bengtsson's slimmer. It can be used to
        compress HTML, XHTML or CSS. It depends on the slimmer module from pypi.
        
        Installation ::
        
            pip install hyde-slimmer
        
        Install Post Processor::
        
            SITE_POST_PROCESSORS = {
                '/': {
                    'hyde_slimmer.site_post_processors.Compress' : {
                        'slimmer': {
                            '*.html': 'html',
                            #'*.html': 'xhtml',
                            #'*.css': 'css',
                        }
                    },
                }
            }
Keywords: hyde html compressor
